<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>TechRM - Soluciones Integrales</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #0b0c10;
            --card-bg: #15161d;
            --card-inner: #1c1d26;
            --card-border: #262835;
            --text-main: #ffffff;
            --text-muted: #8b8e9f;
            --accent-blue: #93c5fd;
            --accent-purple: #d8b4fe;
            --font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-family: var(--font-family);
            line-height: 1.6;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
        }

        /* Navbar */
        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 1.5rem 4rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            background-color: rgba(11, 12, 16, 0.95);
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover, .nav-links a.active {
            color: var(--text-main);
        }
        
        .nav-links a.active {
            border-bottom: 2px solid #3b82f6;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .btn-empezar {
            background-color: #c7d2fe;
            color: #1e1b4b;
            padding: 0.6rem 1.5rem;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: opacity 0.3s;
        }

        .btn-empezar:hover {
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .btn-toggle {
            background-color: transparent;
            color: var(--text-main);
            padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .btn-toggle:hover {
            background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            display: flex;
            height: 100vh;
            width: 100vw;
            margin-top: 0;
            position: relative;
        }

        .hero-half {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 4rem;
            position: relative;
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
        }

        .hero-left {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(11, 12, 16, 0.7), rgba(11, 12, 16, 0.8)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1591488320449-011701bb6704?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1920') center/cover;
            border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
        }

        .hero-right {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(11, 12, 16, 0.7), rgba(11, 12, 16, 0.8)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555066931-4365d14bab8c?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1920') center/cover;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 4vw, 4rem);
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .text-gradient-blue {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #93c5fd, #3b82f6);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .text-gradient-purple {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #e9d5ff, #a855f7);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .hero p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            max-width: 85%;
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .hero-btn {
            padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.2s, opacity 0.2s;
        }

        .hero-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .btn-blue {
            background-color: var(--accent-blue);
            color: #1e3a8a;
        }

        .btn-purple {
            background-color: var(--accent-purple);
            color: #4c1d95;
        }

        /* Sections General */
        section {
            padding: 2rem 0rem;
            max-width: 100%;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .section-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
        }

        .section-subtitle {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #60a5fa;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        /* Unified Solutions */
        .grid-2 {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .card {
            background-color: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 2.5rem;
        }

        .card-blue { border-left: 2px solid #3b82f6; }
        .card-purple { border-left: 2px solid #a855f7; }

        .card-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .card-header h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        /* Inner Cards */
        .inner-items {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .inner-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .inner-card {
            background-color: var(--card-inner);
            padding: 1.25rem;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 1rem;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }
        
        .inner-card:hover {
            background-color: #232530;
        }

        .inner-card-content h4 {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .inner-card-content p {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        .inner-icon {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            flex-shrink: 0;
            margin-top: 0.1rem;
        }

        /* Banner TV */
        .banner-tv {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1.5rem 2.5rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .banner-tv-content {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .banner-tv-text h3 {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .banner-tv-text p {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        .btn-outline-sm {
            background: transparent;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            color: white;
            padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .btn-outline-sm:hover {
            border-color: white;
            background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
        }

        /* Features Section */
        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background-color: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 2.5rem;
        }

        .feature-card svg {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--accent-blue);
        }

        .feature-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }

        .feature-card p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* Bottom Section (Brands + Stats) */
        .bottom-section {
            background-color: #111218;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            padding: 4rem;
        }

        .brands {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto 4rem auto;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            opacity: 0.6;
        }

        .brand-name {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #ffffff;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .why-techrm {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 4rem;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .why-content h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        .why-content p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .stat-box {
            background-color: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 2rem 1rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .stat-value {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        }

        .stat-label {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            padding: 2rem 4rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
        }

        .footer-left strong {
            color: white;
            font-size: 1rem;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
        }

        .footer-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .footer-links a {
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .footer-links a:hover {
            color: white;
        }

        .footer-social {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .footer-social svg {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .footer-social svg:hover {
            color: white;
        }

        /* Light Mode Styles */
        .light-mode {
            --bg-color: #ffffff;
            --card-bg: #f8f9fa;
            --card-inner: #e9ecef;
            --card-border: #dee2e6;
            --text-main: #212529;
            --text-muted: #6c757d;
            --accent-blue: #007bff;
            --accent-purple: #6f42c1;
        }

        .light-mode nav {
            background-color: rgba(248, 249, 250, 0.95);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        .light-mode .nav-links a.active {
            border-bottom: 2px solid #007bff;
        }

        .light-mode .hero-left {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1591488320449-011701bb6704?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1920') center/cover;
        }

        .light-mode .hero-right {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555066931-4365d14bab8c?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1920') center/cover;
        }

        .light-mode .bottom-section {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        .light-mode footer {
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .light-mode .btn-toggle {
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .light-mode .text-gradient-blue {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #000000, #333333);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .light-mode .text-gradient-purple {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #000000, #333333);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .light-mode .hero p {
            color: #495057;
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .hero { flex-direction: column; height: auto; }
            .hero-half { padding: 8rem 2rem 4rem 2rem; }
            .features-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .why-techrm, .grid-2 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .banner-tv { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; gap: 1.5rem; }
            .banner-tv-content { flex-direction: column; }
            .nav-links { display: none; }
            .brands { flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 2rem; justify-content: center; }
            footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem; text-align: center; }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            section, .bottom-section { padding: 4rem 2rem; }
            .inner-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <%- include('navbar') %>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-half hero-left">
            <h1>PRECISIÓN EN<br><span class="text-gradient-blue">HARDWARE.</span></h1>
            <p>Soluciones expertas en montaje de estaciones a medida, reparación técnica avanzada, mantenimiento preventivo y asesoría en optimización de infraestructura.</p>
            <button class="hero-btn btn-blue" onclick="window.location.href='/hardware'">EXPLORAR OPCIONES HARDWARE</button>
        </div>
        
        <div class="hero-half hero-right">
            <h1>EXCELENCIA EN<br><span class="text-gradient-purple">SOFTWARE.</span></h1>
            <p>Desarrollo de ecosistemas digitales: CRM/ERP personalizados, TPVs de alto rendimiento, presencia web escalable y modernización de sistemas heredados.</p>
            <button class="hero-btn btn-purple" onclick="window.location.href='/software'">EXPLORAR OPCIONES SOFTWARE</button>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="servicios">
        <div class="section-header">
            <div class="section-subtitle">NUESTRA EXPERIENCIA</div>
            <h2 class="section-title">Soluciones Unificadas</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid-2">
            <div class="card card-blue">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#93c5fd" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <rect x="4" y="4" width="16" height="16" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
                        <rect x="9" y="9" width="6" height="6"></rect>
                        <line x1="9" y1="1" x2="9" y2="4"></line><line x1="15" y1="1" x2="15" y2="4"></line>
                        <line x1="9" y1="20" x2="9" y2="23"></line><line x1="15" y1="20" x2="15" y2="23"></line>
                        <line x1="20" y1="9" x2="23" y2="9"></line><line x1="20" y1="14" x2="23" y2="14"></line>
                        <line x1="1" y1="9" x2="4" y2="9"></line><line x1="1" y1="14" x2="4" y2="14"></line>
                    </svg>
                    <h3>Hardware & Sistemas</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="inner-items">
                    <div class="inner-card">
                        <svg class="inner-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"></path></svg>
                        <div class="inner-card-content">
                            <h4>Montaje</h4>
                            <p>Estaciones de trabajo a medida.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="inner-card">
                        <svg class="inner-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 2v20M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"></path></svg>
                        <div class="inner-card-content">
                            <h4>Reparación y Mantenimiento</h4>
                            <p>Soporte técnico de alto nivel.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="inner-card">
                        <svg class="inner-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path></svg>
                        <div class="inner-card-content">
                            <h4>Asesorías</h4>
                            <p>Optimización de infraestructura.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card card-purple">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#d8b4fe" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <polyline points="4 17 10 11 4 5"></polyline><line x1="12" y1="19" x2="20" y2="19"></line>
                    </svg>
                    <h3>Desarrollo & Software</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="inner-grid">
                    <div class="inner-card">
                        <div class="inner-card-content">
                            <h4>CRM/ERP</h4>
                            <p>Gestión empresarial robusta.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="inner-card">
                        <div class="inner-card-content">
                            <h4>TPVs</h4>
                            <p>Puntos de venta eficientes.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="inner-card">
                        <div class="inner-card-content">
                            <h4>Páginas Web</h4>
                            <p>Presencia digital escalable.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="inner-card">
                        <div class="inner-card-content">
                            <h4>Modificación</h4>
                            <p>Adaptación de software.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="banner-tv">
            <div class="banner-tv-content">
                <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#c084fc" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="15" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><polyline points="17 2 12 7 7 2"></polyline>
                </svg>
                <div class="banner-tv-text">
                    <h3>HOME TV & ENTRETENIMIENTO</h3>
                    <p>Configuración profesional de centros de entretenimiento y sistemas multimedia domésticos.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <button class="btn-outline-sm">SABER MÁS SOBRE HOME TV</button>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="caracteristicas">
        <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#93c5fd" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path d="M12 2v4"></path><path d="M12 18v4"></path><path d="M4.93 4.93l2.83 2.83"></path><path d="M16.24 16.24l2.83 2.83"></path><path d="M2 12h4"></path><path d="M18 12h4"></path><path d="M4.93 19.07l2.83-2.83"></path><path d="M16.24 7.76l2.83-2.83"></path>
                </svg>
                <h3>Velocidad Pura</h3>
                <p>Latencia cero garantizada en cada línea de código y cada componente.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="feature-card">
                <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#d8b4fe" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path>
                </svg>
                <h3>Seguridad Total</h3>
                <p>Cifrado de grado militar y protección física para tu tranquilidad absoluta.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card">
                <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#fca5a5" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"></path>
                </svg>
                <h3>Calidad Premium</h3>
                <p>Seleccionamos meticulosamente cada componente para un rendimiento óptimo.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="bottom-section">
        <div class="brands">
            <span class="brand-name">NVIDIA</span>
            <span class="brand-name">MICROSOFT</span>
            <span class="brand-name">INTEL</span>
            <span class="brand-name">AWS</span>
            <span class="brand-name">AMD</span>
        </div>

        <div class="why-techrm">
            <div class="why-content">
